translate English day3_fece6a15:


    "\n \"Ha ha ha... Ha ha ha ha ha...!\""


translate English day3_82d5b727:


    "\nI can hear the sound of a woman's laughter coming from somewhere."


translate English day3_631a9ae2:


    "I switch on the light in the dark room and suddenly, my world is flooded with the buzz of the fluorescents. Despite that, my flickering world of grey remains dark."


translate English day3_2a714c8a:


    "She repeatedly calls out to me, and yet I can't answer. It feels like something is covering my mouth, sealing it shut. All I can do is try to endure the smell of rot that permeates the walls of my room and the furniture inside it."


translate English day3_80afc20a:


    "Scarlet fireworks explode in the back of my mind and then vanish."


translate English day3_49304369:


    et "Nothing seems to change, but I can feel someone's presence from within the darkness."


translate English day3_b3d34ae1:



    nvl clear
    "\n\"She probably thinks she can get a status boost by hanging out with me.\""


translate English day3_83c8a052:


    "\nI suppose this is what led to her having such an inflated ego."


translate English day3_1eea3cad:


    "\n\"You were scouted to work here, and yet all you've done from day one is chase women. You truly are the lowest of the lowest scum.\""


translate English day3_624e4295:


    "\"All men are the same--\""


translate English day3_51a706e5:


    et "\nHow the hell am I supposed to prove myself to people who've already made up their minds without knowing anything about who I really am?"


translate English day3_10263686:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Brother [na] will soon be joining our magic circle... so please continue to make them feel welcome here.\""


translate English day3_3efa3074:


    "\nIt was clearly a mistake coming here in the first place. And the longer I stay here, the higher the likelihood of me becoming someone's toy without realizing it."


translate English day3_65825d5c:


    "\n\"See you later, little kittens!\""


translate English day3_98b49f44:


    "\nIf only I'd caught on a little faster that she was simply toying with me..."


translate English day3_7dc7660f:


    et "\n\"We're neighbors, aren't we? I had to say hello.\""


translate English day3_5372bdc0:



    nvl clear
    "\nIf only I'd realized that she was laughing at me for simply existing. But unfortunately, I can't turn back time."


translate English day3_3ba867e6:


    "I'm sure all kinds of folks are already laughing at me for betting my life on some impulsive opportunity, living everyday arrogantly, full of self-conceited pride."


translate English day3_344e6aec:


    "I have no exit strategy. I have nowhere else to turn to."


translate English day3_ec4561f2:


    "\n\"You're so strange..."


translate English day3_b1d78c26:


    "No one's ever said anything like that to me before."


translate English day3_46ae70ae:


    "You're really weird, [na2].\""


translate English day3_659be3a4:


    et "\n..."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_b9064f17:


    br "\nI'm standing on a mound of cold, hard dirt. When I go to move in order to take a look around, the muck sticks to my shoes."


translate English day3_963c9d63:


    extend "\nI lift my foot and realize it's not muck at all--it's animal guts. Mucous membranes from crushed intestines, looking so much like pus, scattered about me."


translate English day3_caef058d:


    extend "\nI'm surrounded by dead bodies. A veritable sea of corpses. Warm blood pours down on me from overhead. I feel like I'm inside someone's grave. Yet I know this place well."


translate English day3_e38456fb:



    nvl clear
    br "\nSuddenly, I look up, and an all too familiar nausea seeps into my ears and through my brain. I see the outline of an angel in the cloudy, white sky.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_3788166a:


    extend "\nIt's almost like the angel is reaching out to me. She's overwhelmingly beautiful."


translate English day3_7f422979:


    extend "\nI feel a reverence toward her, but also a distinct fear. An incredibly appropriate reaction toward a divine being.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_ba521867:


    extend "\nThe angel, which at some point has taken me into her arms, holds a pure white hand over my lower belly. Cold sweat drips from my brow.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_c1bd5080:


    extend "\nShivering uncontrollably, I fearfully bring my hand up to the angel's back. {w}I notice that my skin is stained a muddy red-brown from the blood that poured down onto me."


translate English day3_6f171846:



    nvl clear
    br "\nNo. I can't touch such pure divinity with hands as dirty as mine and yet, her mere presence is irresistible. I can't shake myself free.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_dd5b37dd:


    extend "\nFive elegant, pure, untainted fingers crawl over my body with blasphemous benevolence.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_ca97e800:


    extend "\nThe angel brings her face closer to mine--so close I can't bring myself to breathe."


translate English day3_fc84a7c1:



    nvl clear
    br "\n And then the angel whispers.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_4e58e7fe:


    extend "\n\"I'm tired of this.\"{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_f0d725b6:


    extend "\nWithout giving me time to respond, the angel spreads her white wings wide before vanishing into the distance. Almost simultaneously, I feel something grab my neck, yanking me back toward the earth.{w}{nw}"


translate English day3_b49fed73:


    extend "\nI hear my consciousness shatter as my vision goes dark."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_cf9265f6:


    "\nI wake up with a jerk. Still feeling like I'm asleep, I take in my surroundings, only to find myself looking up at the same old ceiling in the same old room."


translate English day3_dd3154a2:


    "It's pitch-black, the sound of raindrops echoing loudly in the silence. It's raining outside."


translate English day3_0dad6470:


    "I vaguely remember someone telling me once that summer in the capital meant constant rain. {w}Without the sun as a guide, it's hard to tell what time it is. I grope around for the clock by my bedside."


translate English day3_aac77b13:


    "I just wanted to rest my eyes for a moment, but I must've fallen asleep. Less than three hours have passed since the last time I checked."


translate English day3_5cabbe07:


    et "I'm no longer even the least bit sleepy, but I flop back down on the bed anyway."


translate English day3_9941112d:



    nvl clear
    "\n\"That's because you don't know the first thing about women.\""


translate English day3_a73e2dd5:


    "The creak of the old bed springs brings *her* voice to mind."


translate English day3_63cfaf1c:


    "Still lost in a half-remembered reverie, I touch myself, the events from last night trickling down into my consciousness."


translate English day3_60c915e8:


    "I toss and turn restlessly as my mind tries to remember how it felt when her cold hand grazed my waist, the moment when her soft tongue forced its way inside my ear."


translate English day3_2d9aa5fb:


    et "I feel strange. Incomprehensible emotions pin my head down. {w}Are they because of my nightmare, or does everyone feel like this after their first time? Or is it..."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_5a025f00:


    "\n I quickly shut my thoughts down and leave my room. The sound of my door opening and closing along with my footsteps walking down the hall seem louder usual, probably due to the rain."


translate English day3_fd4e134a:


    "It's about time to go to work. But first, I need to clean up the mess from yesterday."


translate English day3_d53beb2a:


    "I open the door to our department office with a vague recollection of what I'd done. {w}However, the scene I'm greeted with is slightly different than how I remember it to be."


translate English day3_0b336675:


    "The dirty vases and broken mugs are still scattered all over the floor, but the shreds of paper and documents that had littered the floor are now gone."


translate English day3_1b161a9f:


    et "Did someone clean them up? My heart freezes in my chest momentarily, but other than that, I remain unfazed. {w}It seems the early morning chill and the dampness in the air have a numbing effect on me."


translate English day3_130e2e39:



    nvl clear
    "\n I simply take out a broom and begin sweeping up the mess on the ground, putting everything in a garbage bag. {w}Seeing all those garbage bags piled in a corner of the room, I can't help but feel sick remembering what the folks here use them for."


translate English day3_31d735c3:


    "Usually the workplace is filled with the stench of burning bodies, but being here so early means there's no smells or sounds to bother me. {w}Even the clock on the wall, ticking away endlessly, is quiet."


translate English day3_7a968a5a:


    "There's probably a group of folks gathered in the department room by now. But I don't want to leave just yet."


translate English day3_780a82a8:


    et "Leaning back against the cool wall, memories from the night before inevitably spring to mind. How am I supposed to prove myself to people who've already made up their minds about who I am without knowing anything about me?"


translate English day3_65d3063f:



    nvl clear
    "\n Staying here means I'll just end up as someone's toy before long, being forced to dance like a puppet for their amusement. I should have seen this ridiculous situation for what it was much, much sooner."


translate English day3_7a3d1cb1:


    "If only I'd realized everyone was laughing at me simply for existing. If I had, I wonder if I could have handled it better."


translate English day3_442941ca:


    "..."


translate English day3_87785018:


    "I hear the faint sound of voices off in the distance. If I stay here any longer, I'll really be in trouble."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_55310e45:


    "\n I shut my thoughts down and spend the rest of the night counting the stains on my bed sheets. At some point, I hear noises coming from next door."


translate English day3_8f866c00:


    "It's definitely time to go to work. The sound of doors opening and closing, the low hum of people talking, and the sound of their footsteps through the hallway seems louder than usual, probably due to the rain."


translate English day3_9bc0e00e:


    "I should be up and getting ready to go, but my body feels almost impossibly heavy."


translate English day3_4e611d35:


    "The reality in front of me seems almost like someone else's problem. I pull the blanket over my head. I don't want to leave this room."


translate English day3_bbbda65f:


    "I jump every time I hear a woman's voice through the door or the wall. I curl up under the covers like a caterpillar in a cocoon."


translate English day3_4a957baf:


    et "I'll just stay here until the noise dies down, I think to myself as I shut my eyes indifferently."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_8a964bb2:



    nvl clear
    "\n As I lay there, waiting patiently for all the sounds to stop, I'm suddenly surprised by a knock on my door. {w}I wait with bated breath underneath the covers before finally approaching the door, moving timidly."


translate English day3_c7505ffd:


    et "It's quiet outside. I ever so gently push the door open, just enough to peek out. After making sure no one is around, I start getting ready for work."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_13bbda84:


    nar "The hallway is deserted. The rain that's been falling steadily since this morning progressively hits the window harder and harder. The dark sky makes the already somber building seem bigger than usual."


translate English day3_29373c56:


    nar "I slink past the department's main room, turn the corner, and immediately come face to face with the last person I want to see right now."


translate English day3_285c026f:


    nar "Seemingly just as a surprised to see me, he stares at me silently for a moment before scowling."


translate English day3_8a9680a1:


    sc "You again..."


translate English day3_a9d1110c:


    sc "Could you try not to add more work to my plate? What are you up to this time, aside from slacking off?"


translate English day3_72370441:


    pl "Uh? Oh... Sorry."


translate English day3_3303b609:


    sc "If this is the way you work, then go ahead and find a different position."


translate English day3_6db1bc01:


    sc "I took care of the job you decided to leave half-finished and then went home... If you don't feel like working here, then we can find you something else to do."


translate English day3_fff5448d:


    nar "With that, Securett begins hurrying toward the department office."


translate English day3_69344011:


    nar "Most people are happy enough with slinging petty insults, but this guy isn't satisfied unless he gets in that last infuriating word--just like pouring salt on an open, unhealed wound."


translate English day3_4f8b6333:


    nar "Thanks to him, I'm in an even worse mood than before. Where's he in such a rush to get to anyway?"


translate English day3_6e16b1fc:


    pl "Look, about yesterday..."


translate English day3_b1ba8b68:


    sc "What about it?"


translate English day3_b43d3ee3:


    pl "Actually, forget it. Looks like you've been running around all morning."


translate English day3_0f727768:


    pl "Did you run over here just to... look for me?"


translate English day3_bc8899ce:


    sc "...I'm simply following orders."


translate English day3_0a3615e0:


    pl "You've been running around all morning, huh?"


translate English day3_6694f52a:


    sc "Yes, thanks to you."


translate English day3_a69d0419:


    nar "There's an uneasy pause. If I filled the silence, then the conversation would undoubtedly continue, but I'm not sure if I'm in the mood for that."


translate English day3_d4f52c74:


    nar "The awkward silence is filled with the sound of two people passing through the hallway. Suddenly, he speaks up."


translate English day3_17fdbd94:


    sc "I'm asking you to be extra careful today. We have a guest coming."


translate English day3_62cf5f87:


    pl "A guest? What do you mean?"


translate English day3_bdb94677:


    nar "He just looks at me, silently. If you didn't want to answer, then you should've kept your mouth shut from the beginning, you freakin' weirdo."


translate English day3_df1a9dee:


    nar "As if sensing my frustration, he suddenly stops, peering at me out of the corner of his eye."


translate English day3_30a62821:


    nar "I hear his words before I have time to panic."


translate English day3_26258028:


    sc "A benefactor. One of several willing to help us by donating not just money, but material goods and time as well."


translate English day3_2c850de6:


    sc "Originally, the Health Department was in charge of distributing donations to believers, but..."


translate English day3_f5d537a7:


    pl "But...?"


translate English day3_fff33c94:


    sc "..."


translate English day3_c13a446d:


    pl "Sorry, I couldn't quite catch that. Can you repeat what you said?"


translate English day3_a13ee738:


    sc "Forget it... You don't really need to know any of this. "


translate English day3_85fe958d:


    sc "All that matters is you do exactly what you're told if any of these benefactors are around. "


translate English day3_52c9da20:


    sc "And if any of them try talking to you, don't deviate from the script. If any of them start to become interested, it'll cause..."


translate English day3_603df4ce:


    sc "...a whole lot of trouble."


translate English day3_cc2b47a1:


    nar "He speaks so quietly and always slurs his words, making his voice sound abrasive to me."


translate English day3_b0f9789f:


    nar "He pauses mid-sentence before lowering his voice, speaking even quieter than usual. This only makes it worse, as I'm already straining to understand him."


translate English day3_cc24c15f:


    nar "Good grief. This guy is such an asshole. If you looked up \"trouble\" in the dictionary, his picture would be there. "


translate English day3_69884842:


    nar "Honestly, I'm pretty confident in my ability to deal with troublesome adults."


translate English day3_a54e8f6c:


    nar "As folks get older, their thinking gets simpler and their actions follow likewise."


translate English day3_404d0159:


    nar "All you need to do is butter them up and they quickly become putty in your hands."


translate English day3_2e3bf984:


    nar "Securett reaches the door to the main department office before, the noise from inside audible from all the way down the hall."


translate English day3_1b937835:


    nar "Walking in together, I immediately grab the attention of a brown-haired woman who walks over, heels clacking noisily."


translate English day3_2d01ccd7:


    lz1 "..."


translate English day3_2f0e8d97:


    nar "She plants herself wordlessly in front of me, glaring at me. "


translate English day3_f0b63423:


    nar "Securett glances at me out of the corner of his eye before quickly walking past us."


translate English day3_c78df32b:


    lz1 "Quit."


translate English day3_c4ddbe41:


    nar "She snaps at me, leaving an awkward silence hanging over us. She comes at me out of nowhere, commanding me to quit. I look at her, completely taken aback, unsure if I heard her correctly."


translate English day3_bee8e75b:


    nar "Seeing my confusion, she repeats what she said except louder and slower, her visible disgust for me even stronger."


translate English day3_41588bb0:


    lz1 "Q-U-I-T. Understand? I told you to QUIT! Didn't you hear me?!"


translate English day3_1b46f02c:


    nar "Not waiting for an answer, she slaps my arm in an attempt at shoving me aside before stalking out."


translate English day3_f794eedd:


    nar "She'd clearly gone out of her way in order to confront me out of spite. I pat the arm that she smacked on her way out."


translate English day3_599ac56f:


    nar "She very clearly hadn't held back, but regardless, she's still a tiny girl, much smaller than me. And yet I couldn't shake the lingering discomfort, like gum stuck to the bottom of a shoe."


translate English day3_e9d3c7c3:


    nar "I gain nothing by being conspicuously late. If anything, I'll only make things even more awkward than they already are, which is the last thing I want."


translate English day3_011e1568:


    nar "Avoiding the flurry of people around me, I quietly slip over to my designated spot. "


translate English day3_0cae07bc:


    nar "I'm a pretty unlucky guy by default, but knowing I've brought this string of bad luck onto myself makes it worse."


translate English day3_40c6c811:


    my "[na2]...?"


translate English day3_80a70e99:


    nar "Sighing under the weight of my bad decisions, I hear my name, her voice as effervescent as a soap bubble."


translate English day3_e2df9ef6:


    nar "My expression immediately brightens on seeing that familiar face for the first time today."


translate English day3_4e45ea83:


    pl "Oh, Maya! You're here early."


translate English day3_7f195776:


    my "Not really... You're the one that's late... Though it looks like my sister just left..."


translate English day3_14dbbefe:


    pl "Yeah, I ran into her a minute ago, in fact. She seems in a worse mood than usual. She didn't say anything to you, did she?"


translate English day3_701c867b:


    my "We weren't exactly having a conversation or anything, but... well... we were wondering if you were maybe hanging out with that blonde girl and that's why you weren't here..."


translate English day3_6fa86165:


    nar "My smile momentarily vanishes. Probably because I never would have imagined Maya, of all people, being the one to ask me about that."


translate English day3_1ece5fcd:


    nar "I might not know her very well, but I figured I had a clear enough picture painted of the type of girl she is."


translate English day3_d1efdc10:


    nar "Quickly regaining control of my countenance, I open my mouth to speak. I shudder at the thought of her agonizing over this, even if momentarily."


translate English day3_1918416a:


    pl "Oh... Haha! I was... uh... just not feeling the greatest."


translate English day3_ac18d53c:


    pl "I'm still not used to the pillows they have here... Oh! And the time difference doesn't help, either."


translate English day3_6dd56a5d:


    my "I see..."


translate English day3_20f40940:


    pl "More importantly!"


translate English day3_9a7b6e24:


    nar "I clap my hands together before crouching down to get closer to her height. Her shoulders tremble as she looks at me out of the corner of her eyes, wide-open with worry."


translate English day3_ab0e4830:


    nar "Feeling a pang of guilt over seeing her in that state, I lower my voice before responding."


translate English day3_e04c6d42:


    pl "Did something happen? That jerk, Securett, mentioned something to me about some kind of guest. He made it seem like kind of a big deal."


translate English day3_6d580e07:


    my "Oh, uh... well, about that..."


translate English day3_50737b01:


    nar "Maya wordlessly drops her gaze."


translate English day3_5da5be8a:


    nar "Anyone would be put off seeing her look this miserable, but at least I'm not the reason for it."


translate English day3_1cf69ea5:


    nar "I follow her gaze to see a small child standing next to her. I'm not sure how long she's been there, but she has a firm grip on Maya's arm."


translate English day3_c186bedd:


    nar "A little taller than three feet, {w}the girl has long baby-blue curls that are beautifully styled."


translate English day3_515d662d:


    nar "The well-ironed and formal attire she's wearing paints her with a dignified time-worn look missing from the other priests."


translate English day3_92ebdbf4:


    nar "Her appearance clashes completely with our surroundings, making her seem otherwordly, almost like she's a porcelain doll come to life."


translate English day3_2f4cc25a:


    nar "I notice her eyes on me. Where in the world did this young rich girl come from?"


translate English day3_e11c95cd:


    pl "\"Who are you...?\""


translate English day3_d362629f:


    nar "The words are barely out of my mouth before her jewel-like eyes light up. {w}She then immediately latches onto my arm before yanking up my sleeve."


translate English day3_4e67843a:


    nar "Her reaction is so unexpected that I topple over in surprise, bringing the girl down with me. She doesn't seem to care, however, evidenced by the fact that her hands never stop moving."


translate English day3_1e070460:


    pl "Whah?!"


translate English day3_39a22647:


    qus "Wuh.."


translate English day3_7b70cfd5:


    qus "Waaaaaah!!!" with sshake


translate English day3_799cd871:


    qus "You're the dark-skinned boy I heard so much about with the seraphic black hair that shines like obsidian! Oh, and red eyes that burn as passionately as the sun itself!"


translate English day3_28638d26:


    qus "You hail from the outside world, yes?"


translate English day3_bc7065ef:


    nar "She's shouting at a volume you'd never expect from such a quiet-looking girl, her overly enthused curiosity upon meeting me"


translate English day3_28b03461:


    nar "for the first time akin to how one might treat a dog or a cat."


translate English day3_3eaa49bd:


    nar "As her hands move restlessly--from my arms to my face, running through my hair, then over my ears and down to my stomach--with barely a pause to catch her breath, I find myself getting angry."


translate English day3_44d9e71f:


    pl "Hey..."


translate English day3_66c9d7d8:


    qus "Wow! I've never seen an actual outsider before!" with sshake


translate English day3_2dbcd1e4:


    qus "Your skin's so smooth and firm. And then it's cool and hard in certain places, almost like clay!"


translate English day3_cccf87e4:


    qus "Overall, you're pretty well-built. You've got the healthy body commonly seen in agrarian society, as depicted in textbooks!"


translate English day3_52c679ce:


    qus "Though you're a tad shorter than I imagined, and your belly's a bit soft..."


translate English day3_795dd998:


    qus "Oh no! You've got a little pudge on you! Wait, are you holding your breath? Go ahead and relax!"


translate English day3_4543e6d6:


    qus "Ten fingernails, which is to be expected, and... Oh! Are these bandages on your arm just normal bandages? Can you take them off for me?!"


translate English day3_be976ba8:


    pl "Excuse me...!!!"


translate English day3_824db18b:


    nar "The moment I open my mouth to protest, she immediately grabs my jaw with both hands."


translate English day3_7ab56766:


    nar "The feeling of being forced into this position suddenly brings an unwanted memory to mind."


translate English day3_6f874bf4:


    nar "Sticky hands running from my face to my back and then over my chest. Cool fingers pressed against my cheeks, forcing my mouth open. I find myself growing faint as discomfort swells inside me."


translate English day3_cf401674:


    qus "Your tongue and teeth are the same light color as the people here! Fascinating, truly fascinating! I wonder if the number of teeth is the same? Though your bite seems a bit irregular..."


translate English day3_d9dff5aa:


    qus "Oh! My inquisitive mind is dancing with the need for knowledge!" with sshake


translate English day3_9fe14c2a:


    qus "Any chance you're free right now? Because I'd love to take you somewhere that's a bit darker... just the two of us... " with sshake


translate English day3_6854d422:


    extend "There's no way I'd make you s-s-strip down in public, of course! Nothing indecent, I swear!" with sshake


translate English day3_de47b0a7:


    nar "Mustering all the strength in my tensed-up body, I brusquely shake her hands off me."


translate English day3_d5b0e9d9:


    pl "What's wrong with you?! I'm not your pet!" with vpunch


translate English day3_f88e9a4a:


    qus "Oh..."


translate English day3_4147b05f:


    pl "You're being really rude! Touching a total stranger's body without permission is creepy! Knock it off!!!"


translate English day3_f4dd9e89:


    nar "I spit my words out with such venom that even I'm a little flustered by my reaction. How did I let this girl get so under my skin?"


translate English day3_a93cf00c:


    my "C-Claire..."


translate English day3_4ffac622:


    nar "The usual chaos in the department room is suddenly replaced by silence. Feeling the weight of everyone's attention on me, I force my inflamed temper down, returning to my typical calm demeanor."


translate English day3_450e463a:


    nar "Being the center of attention is hard enough,"


translate English day3_93fe8582:


    nar "but having a tough guy like me seemingly threatening a young girl like her doesn't seem great from any angle."


translate English day3_9685623d:


    ex1 "How scary!"


translate English day3_a6c236b6:


    nar "I hear someone speak up from somewhere behind us, only adding to the subdued atmosphere."


translate English day3_a2fc038c:


    nar "The comment is followed up by a glib whistle, and I realize there's nothing I can do except try and slow down my out of control breathing."


translate English day3_f70c97e9:


    nar "{nw}"


translate English day3_c6c0b185:


    qus "I'm sorry..."


translate English day3_0cbc094d:


    my "Um... I'm really sorry. He's not usually like this..."


translate English day3_f671f253:


    qus "It's okay, Miss Maya. That was an obvious faux pas on my part."


translate English day3_68158a92:


    qus "My sincerest apologies, Man From the Outside World. I am deeply ashamed of my uncouth actions, tarnishing the Myosotis name."


translate English day3_69e28169:


