    nar "It's a habit she probably picked up in response to undesirable situations, creating her own mental shadows where she can hide."


translate English day3_9564abaf:


    nar "And as evidence of this, when I look into her eyes, hidden beneath her thin eyelashes,"


translate English day3_e83ebf1d:


    nar "she keeps her mouth shut, her gaze unfocused."


translate English day3_8b97de14:


    nar "But there are times where she's able to look people right in the face. "


