    nar "I have no idea what's wrong, and I can't ask her, either."


translate English day3_669bb0bf:


    nar "..."


translate English day3_f7de351f:


    "\n Something bumps against my foot and I look down to see a human head. {w}It's the head of a total stranger, trapped in an eternal expression of wide-eyed shock, their skin rough and pockmarked."


