    sc "It's difficult trying to jump into a cleanup job halfway through, plus she'll probably be helping out the Health Department for the rest of the day."


translate English day3_55f04b80:


    pl "So that's the problem? Sounds like Maya to me, a textbook people pleaser..."


translate English day3_62aaf1bf:


    sc "Are you even listening to me? Sometimes, I wonder what goes through your mind..."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_4f3a62af:


    "\n I hear the quiet voice of a young man {w}coming from a group of ministers blocking the entrance."


translate English day3_bff5e72d:


    "After giving a curt response, Securett shoots me a look that seems to say \"come here.\""


