    et "Securett, who's pulled down the cloth covering his mouth, briefly explains the situation before bringing out some keepsakes we found."


translate English day3_5ddb85e6:



    nvl clear
    "\n He mentions the cause of death being a combination of shock from a heart attack and the constant cold--the cause of many deaths lately among the elderly. {w}His house was quite small, meaning he didn't own many things."


