    "Upon seeing a particular framed picture, he drops his gaze, his body shaking all over."


translate English day3_8ec62462:


    "I've never seen this man before in my life, but it's obvious that his suffering outweighs his grief."


translate English day3_d3123b54:


    "He can't simply mourn the passing of his father. He'll probably have to deal with some other internal issues first."


