    nar "And yet he always seems to shut down our conversations in the vaguest of ways."


translate English day3_b24c9cde:


    nar "I catch a whiff of the deodorant before Securett hands it to me."


translate English day3_a82d50f6:


    nar "It's got a faint floral scent, maybe something more akin to grass than flowers. Regardless, I've definitely smelled it before."


translate English day3_3d131219:


    "\n I follow close behind him, his numerous complaints circling through my head, {w}when suddenly, POW!!!"


