    "\"You priests are disgusting! Incompetent pieces of shit who live off the backs of the poor, taxing them to death! How DARE you show your faces here!\""


translate English day3_59e0b78c:


    et "I hear a gruff male voice from somewhere behind me. He sounds pissed."


