    "You stand by and watch people die, only interested in saving your own skin as you lick the mud from the Cardinal's boots! You're nothing more than shameless beggars!\""


translate English day3_8f50a9a1:


    "\"I'm sorry you feel that way. I'm truly sorry.\""


translate English day3_b9bf5cf3:


    "\"The maggots wriggling in that old man's corpse are more pure than you bottom-feeders will ever be!"


