    pl "That's not what I'm talking about at all! Why were they so angry at us, specifically? I've never seen them before in my life..."


translate English day3_6706c249:


    sc "*sigh*..."


translate English day3_2a9654ab:


    sc "I have no idea what kind of life you've been leading until now, but this place isn't like where you're from. "


