    sc "Honestly, you rookies have done such a shoddy job thus far that we'd be better off without you."


translate English day3_fd02b37d:


    pl "The work is what it is, but that sarcasm of yours is the hardest to handle, Cue."


translate English day3_8761dc98:


    sc "...Don't give people weird nicknames."


