translate English day3_7cd1afa5:


    sc "Tch, I never heard anything about this."


translate English day3_9783b71d:


    pl "Because I hadn't told you."


translate English day3_831534de:


    pl "See? This is what happens when you don't tell people things ahead of time."


translate English day3_f945c9c7:


    pl "You can tag along if you don't believe me. The bishop from the Cleanup Department should be there, too."


translate English day3_a79b1627:


    sc "*sigh*..."


translate English day3_c535cfe3:


    nar "Securett, who's been shooting me a death glare, his brows furrowed, suddenly looks away before shaking his head."


translate English day3_8d568fe0:


    nar "It seems there's some truth to the rumors, with the bishop clearly being a sore spot for him. "


translate English day3_60fe6dba:


    nar "Not that it matters to me at all right now."


translate English day3_b02177f7:


    sc "From now on, if you have any other business that interferes with your work schedule, you tell me. Understood?"


translate English day3_4f221a70:


    pl "Sure, sure. Thanks bunches."


translate English day3_332a031d:


    nar "Without waiting for an answer, he turns and walks off back to the department office. I'm filled with distaste for him, though no stronger than any other day."


translate English day3_992af6e9:


    nar "I watch him walk off for a moment before turning around in the opposite direction."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_75d718f4:


    "\n Despite this being the first time I'm going to the Magic Department on my own, I managed to make it without getting lost."


translate English day3_7465ecc9:


    "The prestige the department holds certainly helped."


translate English day3_84d2770a:


    "The luxurious carpet, free of dust, the giant table in the center of the room, the overbearingly bright golden ornaments that perfectly contrast the dark walls... "


translate English day3_7a4616e9:


    "Compared to the sterile Cleanup Department, the difference is enough to make you laugh out loud."


translate English day3_77ba5d84:


    "A quick knock followed by \"come in.\" My mind conjures up images of an empty room but a man answers in a firm voice, allowing me entry."


translate English day3_1860a473:


    et "He's sitting in a particularly high-backed chair, and despite the sudden appearance of a guest, remains motionless, his attention fixed on the papers in his hands."


translate English day3_e1a14adb:



    nvl clear
    "\n The man looks up and, upon seeing me, the stern scowl on his face softens."


translate English day3_6baf0957:


    "\"Oh, it's you. That's fine. Come on over.\""


translate English day3_21ffc886:


    "The heaviness in the air usually has a calming effect on me, although in here, it feels more oppressive than usual, pressing down on my soul for seemingly no reason at all."


translate English day3_6aa3c573:


    "Erzsebet Alternata. I find it hard to refer to the bishop, who looks almost toddler-esque in appearance, as a man."


translate English day3_9bae1f20:


    et "While still living in my village far outside the capital, he paid us a visit one day, out of the blue, which is when he first explained the curious nature of his appearance to me."


translate English day3_32af9759:



    nvl clear
    "\n For as long as I can remember, I've heard that power borrowed from God always comes with significant price. "


translate English day3_235f6065:


    et "That his appearance is a direct result of this exchange isn't all that hard to fathom."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_14:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_d53cfb27:


    er "I heard you'd arrived safely,"


translate English day3_b44777b3:


    extend " and yet this appears to be our first face-to-face meeting."


translate English day3_c0585244:


    pl "It's true. I wanted to come here straight away, but I was dumped in a different department without a single explanation."


translate English day3_661eb42d:


    pl "That wasn't the deal, right? Do you know what's going on?"


translate English day3_b9d2b9a6:


    er "I guess they didn't tell you anything, hrm? "


translate English day3_de2884e1:


    er "You see, the Disposal Team you belong to was originally affiliated with the Magic Department. We used to work together."


translate English day3_80ee0bb4:


    er "Words are not enough, but essentially, it would've been unusual for the Magic Department, which prides itself on only employing those with strong bloodlines and connections,"


translate English day3_c8e04a58:


    er " to take in an outsider who doesn't even know the capital's geography. "


translate English day3_718a5445:


    er "I figured this way, the appropriate protocols would be met, but..."


translate English day3_185775ae:


    er "Are you unhappy with your position?"


translate English day3_413f3e3b:


    pl "I mean, it is the Disposal Team..."


translate English day3_6778f0c7:


    er "Don't get me wrong, leaving you in that vile nest of inbreds brings me no great joy, "


translate English day3_10cdadf8:


    er "but unfortunately, that's how it goes sometimes."


translate English day3_b52d5cca:


    er "Though I hope their vulgar behavior doesn't wash off on you."


translate English day3_165c9ba3:


    pl "Wow... I take it you don't like the Cleanup Department that much."


translate English day3_72ded1e9:


    er "I utterly despise them."


translate English day3_61e09975:


    er "Not like any of them are worth my time, of course! I'm too busy to be bothered by their mere existence."


translate English day3_d36c34df:


    er "Please don't misunderstand me, though. I don't tend to ostracize people based on my personal bias towards them."


translate English day3_52fdea04:


    er "Everything happens for a reason, you understand?"


translate English day3_f70048d8:


    nar "Despite his arrogant tone and conservative manner, his inclination toward talking about people behind their backs makes him sound like the department girls engaging in gossip."


translate English day3_3ed22836:


    er "Why are you staring at me like that? Have something you'd like to say?"


translate English day3_f47df77b:


    pl "Not really. Well, aside from wondering why you enjoy looking like a child."


translate English day3_7c2e15bc:


    er "When there's something you want desperately, you're willing to pay whatever price is necessary to get it. That side effects of such mean I now defy the passage of time forever."


translate English day3_ef8b91d9:


    pl "Mm-hm... In other words, you're going backwards?"


translate English day3_e378b896:


    er "Exactly. Well, almost. You're pretty sharp... hm. Just as I thought. My hunches are never wrong."


translate English day3_ab3834c6:


    nar "The only kind of adult you should look up to is one who ends every thought praising themselves."


translate English day3_3cff79b1:


    er "What's this? It's already been about a week, hrm? "


translate English day3_79aa308e:


    er "You have until your Rite of Ordination to learn all about the temple and its geography. "


translate English day3_47abbe20:


    er "Get accustomed to carrying out your job smoothly and take in as much as you can from my dear Arne."


translate English day3_88d0e5c9:


    er "That's all. Anything other than that is unimportant."


translate English day3_272a4a1c:


    pl "Wow. I heard you're a pretty important person around here, and yet this seems like an incredibly kind gesture. "


translate English day3_1628c7f3:


    pl "What's really going on?"


translate English day3_daec7cef:


    er "As I said when we first met, the continuation of the Magic Department depends on you."


translate English day3_c941c2ec:


    er "What's important for now is getting you in... Once that happens, as long as you maintain an exemplory record and gather a large flock of believers, "


translate English day3_4bafe369:


    er "your partner, Arne, will take care of the rest."


translate English day3_d7a3489d:


    pl "Wait... Hold on a minute! Partner? Like married spouse?!"


translate English day3_33571af7:


    er "Of course. You really are quick to pick up on things."


translate English day3_408dbaa0:


    er "The reason why the Alternatas have maintained such an exalted position throughout history is because of our divine power, far stronger than any other..."


translate English day3_e032c55c:


    er "and that power flows through *your* veins."


translate English day3_c660a7b2:


    pl "I'm not sure what you mean... I only have two stigmata."


translate English day3_2ea9d420:


    er "I'm referring to the potential that currently lies dormant within you."


translate English day3_10d7a8f4:


    pl "The potential..."


translate English day3_020d2b7b:


    nar "I was wondering what was going on, and it turns out to be more ridiculous than I was prepared for."


translate English day3_11abec94:


    nar "I'm the one who blindly accepted an invitation by a total stranger and came here, of my own free will, without asking even one single question about it."


translate English day3_4d95d3e7:


    nar "That I put my entire life on the line for a reckless gamble is, in itself, pretty ballsy."


translate English day3_dbb16c54:


    nar "But I guess this also means the Magic Department's continued existence is on the line."


translate English day3_a29e0623:


    pl "While everything you've said sounds promising so far, how can you be sure I'll agree to doing any of this?"


translate English day3_8362c874:


    er "The possibility of you turning down my offer? Hrm... Interesting. I'm the one who stuck my neck out in order to bring you here. "


translate English day3_bc823d70:


    er "No one would be foolish enough to complain about being handed a free ride."


translate English day3_f0a81575:


    nar "His commanding tone of voice echoes loudly in the room, my sense of obligation growing heavier along with it. "


translate English day3_c42ed0a1:


    nar "I'm pretty pissed about a number of things, but if I can't control my anger, everything ends here."


translate English day3_05f5d8c4:


    pl "I see. Thanks, Bishop. So I'll take that to mean I'm free to wander around the temple grounds whenever I want then?"


translate English day3_3bc2e01c:


    er "Let's not overcomplicate things. I, Erzsebet Alternata, grant you permission to come and go as you please. With that said..."


translate English day3_c0f0db4d:


    er "The temple is not without its fair share of... eccentrics, shall we say. You'd do well not to get involved in their affairs. Now then, is there a special spot you have in mind?"


translate English day3_555fad33:


    pl "Not exactly, but it seems like there are many interesting places throughout the temple. Like the Training Room, for example, or the Infirmary, or the Library."


translate English day3_0b442116:


    er "Do not mingle with the unhealed patients in the Infirmary. Their slothfulness will cause your own senses to dull."


translate English day3_90cb6434:


    er "The Library, however... It's true that you clearly lack in knowledge regarding the capital, and it's important that you make up for it."


translate English day3_e532fad8:


    er "However, the Academics have an inclination for writing poetry, so keep on your toes."


translate English day3_bc17a40b:


    pl "Poetry...?"


translate English day3_013248f8:


    er "Perhaps I was a bit too vague, so let me try again. Put simply, they've all got a screw or two loose. The Academic Department is like a den of snakes."


translate English day3_0f3e32a6:


    er "Otherwise... ahem! As I mentioned previously, start forming a closer relationship with Arne."


translate English day3_ad5f31cc:


    pl "I'll be sure to do that."


translate English day3_45aca161:


    er "Just what I want to hear. Now then, it's about time you were off."


translate English day3_83d6681c:


    nar "Seemingly satisfied with my answer, he once again picks up his papers."


translate English day3_0b84c584:


    er "Love one another, as God loves you."


translate English day3_5e06213c:


    nar "I strain to keep a smile on my face, the corners of my mouth quivering, until the door is shut behind me."


translate English day3_53a9b8db:


    nar "I finally let out the breath I was holding. He might look like an adorable young boy, but hidden inside is an absolutely heartless old geezer!"


translate English day3_6e068982:


    en "Oh, gosh! There you are! I've been looking all over for you!"


translate English day3_222f1101:


    nar "As I limp out, dragging my tired feet behind me, I find myself greeted familiarly by a rather tall man."


translate English day3_5e3c2a09:


    pl "Didn't we just meet yesterday? Why were you looking for me?"


translate English day3_bc4c1b09:


    en "I heard you had a meeting with the bishop, right? You just looked so lost about everything yesterday... "


translate English day3_0c92110b:


    en "so I was really worried about you!"


translate English day3_1e25c28e:


    en "Looks like you're all done then? A one-on-one meeting with the bishop must've been rough..."


translate English day3_e2ae51eb:


    en "But he seems to really like you, [na]! Honestly, just thinking about it makes my stomach turn..."


translate English day3_554936d4:


    pl "Seriously..."


translate English day3_22ffa361:


    pl "To be honest, I'm still trying to wrap my head around everything. It's hard for me to feel proud about any of this when I'm not sure if this benefits me in any way..."


translate English day3_6f7a4293:


    pl "But I think it should be okay... Though I really had no idea what I was getting myself into!"


translate English day3_ca773768:


    en "That you share this magical bloodline is all that really matters."


translate English day3_7206c9e4:


    en "Whether you believe it or not, the divine power chose you. Magic literally runs through your veins, [na]."


translate English day3_fb82e36e:


    en "Which is why you gotta make sure your actions and behavior reflect that power. "


translate English day3_587cbb81:


    en "Speaking of which, I heard you snapped at Lady Clione this morning."


translate English day3_f059579a:


    pl "Eeep! How do you know about THAT?!" with sshake


translate English day3_0c325961:


    en "Word spreads fast in the temple, especially when it comes to Claire!"


translate English day3_a89869cb:


    en "She can strip a person down in seconds... figuratively *and* literally!"


translate English day3_ecaa4a4e:


    en "But she loves hanging out here. In fact, she's probably still around somewhere."


translate English day3_6771dc59:


    pl "Hrm..."


translate English day3_fb383e6c:


    pl "So, did you need me for something? Were you really looking for me because you were worried? Or is this about something else?"


translate English day3_a6c3e9ee:


    en "Er... Well, actually, I wanted to apologize about how I treated you yesterday."


translate English day3_1335b7a5:


    en "You've got it all wrong, though! I'm not a heartless jerk! I hope you can believe me. It's just..."


translate English day3_ac9ca803:


    pl "No need to stress. Just tell me what's up."


translate English day3_cde284da:


    nar "As I wait for his answer, my eyes scan his face silently, looking for a sign. Constantly reading people's expressions is starting to get exhausting."


translate English day3_60b5908e:


    nar "He still seems distressed over the incident from the other day."


translate English day3_cae59804:


    nar "I can tell from the way he touches his neck that it's been preying on his mind and that he feels embarrassed about it."


translate English day3_9e6ce7f0:


    nar "He briefly lowers his gaze as he chooses his words carefully. Then, as if making up his mind, he clears his throat and opens his mouth to speak."


translate English day3_320ffcf0:


    en "So... I'm sorry for answering a question with a question, but..."


translate English day3_9b6f6fb0:


    en "If I may ask... What's your honest opinion of my older sister?"


translate English day3_ea216aa0:


    nar "I definitely wasn't expecting that, but my answer quickly springs to mind."


translate English day3_76b2fe88_15:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_76b2fe88_16:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_76b2fe88_17:


    nvl clear


translate English day3_q_ar_e59a4249:


    pl "You mean Arnie? I like her a lot. She's a really good person."


translate English day3_q_ar_c869dce1:


    nar "He seems bewildered for a moment at my answer before beaming at me happily."


translate English day3_q_ar_1e83be07:


    nar "I only talked to her for a brief moment, but that was more than enough to get a read on her character."


translate English day3_q_ar_1471dd3a:


    nar "She's the type of person who gets along with everyone and who is seemingly impossible to hate."


translate English day3_q_ar_ba75dcf7:


    nar "I still have my doubts about the crude bishop, and while he is pretty gross, none of his personality seems to have rubbed off on her."


translate English day3_q_ar_73f97122:


    en "Oh yeah?"


translate English day3_q_ar_c6ff9575:


    en "Well, great!"


translate English day3_q_ar_652d4392:


    en "And of course she's great!"


translate English day3_q_ar_e7ebc82a:


    extend " Honestly, I was prepared to beat you to a pulp if you said even one bad word about her!"


translate English day3_q_ar_3a9e610a:


    pl "No violence, please!"


translate English day3_q_ar_8aaf32b3:


    en "Haha! I'm just joking!"


translate English day3_q_ar_4ffbf62d:


    en "Take good care of her, okay? "


translate English day3_q_ar_6fb0f0dd:


    en "Also, I don't mind if you start referring to me as your big brother."


translate English day3_q_ar_e6a228c7:


    pl "Huh? Why?"


translate English day3_q_ar_efc79ea6:


    en "Um, well..."


translate English day3_q_ar_d18222fa:


    pl "Hahaha! I'm just playing with you! Thanks, bro."


translate English day3_q_ar_d5a8a62c:


    en "Whew..."


translate English day3_q_ar_577121cf:


    pl "As your sister, you must know her pretty well, right?"


translate English day3_q_ar_61ebebc2:


    en "I might not know everything about Arne, but I know plenty..."


translate English day3_q_ar_17abfd69:


    pl "Oh, yeah? Well, I still don't know anything about her!"


translate English day3_q_ar_5cab8f09:


    nar "And we're gonna get married, huh?"


translate English day3_q_ar_71b60aea:


    nar "I'm still pretty lukewarm about the whole thing. To be honest, marriage isn't something I've ever really thought about,"


translate English day3_q_ar_d78e35e9:


    nar "and frankly, it's not really something I want any part of."


translate English day3_q_ar_6cca2eac:


    nar "And of course, my opinion on the matter hasn't changed, even now. But thinking about it brings a question to mind. "


translate English day3_q_ar_f4be132e:


    nar "Does she know about any of this?"


translate English day3_q_ar_6ffd261a:


    nar "Was she so nice to me the other day because she knew? And if so, what does she think about me?"


translate English day3_q_ar_c2e18f3c:


    nar "As thoughts of her fill my mind, I find myself growing slightly more depressed."


translate English day3_q_ar_ff476e23:


    pl "Speaking of which, I was thinking of paying her a little visit."


translate English day3_q_ar_7f1714fb:


    en "That's a great idea! She was really worried about you, too, [na]."


translate English day3_q_ar_572e1a04:


    nar "If I'm going to untangle my feelings for her, it'll probably help to go talk to her in person."


translate English day3_q_rs_72f6f463:


    pl "How I feel about your sister? Well..."


translate English day3_q_rs_cd4a936e:


    pl "Truth be told, I'm not sure yet. I'm not the one to form an opinion on someone I just met yesterday."


translate English day3_q_rs_1cd9992d:


    nar "His face darkens slightly at my response."


translate English day3_q_rs_30183ce3:


    nar "She seems like a really nice person. I certainly don't hate her. But I don't like her, either."


translate English day3_q_rs_8f8379fa:


    nar "To be fair, right now all I can picture is the face of the bishop, who I'm already pretty fed up with."


translate English day3_q_rs_73f97122:


    en "Oh yeah?"


translate English day3_q_rs_9c70e371:


    nar "He hesitantly makes eye contact with me, as if aware of the situation."


translate English day3_q_rs_ee85c147:


    en "You seem different from yesterday. Did something happen?"


translate English day3_q_rs_8c841121:


    pl "Well, actually, a lot has happened, but I'm not sure if I feel comfortable talking about it... "


translate English day3_q_rs_b73834ae:


    pl "Mainly I'm just exhausted from working all day."


translate English day3_q_rs_6b872883:


    en "I g-guess I don't seem like someone you can trust, huh?"


translate English day3_q_rs_27f883ba:


    pl "I mean, I only just met you yesterday, right?"


translate English day3_q_rs_cf162dec:


    en "Mm..."


translate English day3_q_rs_8a9fa16b:


    nar "I'm still pretty lukewarm about the whole thing. To be honest, marriage isn't something I've ever really thought about,"


translate English day3_q_rs_eb5697cd:


    nar "and frankly, it's not really something I want any part of."


translate English day3_q_rs_e59e7891:


    nar "I try to shake off the annoyance that's slowly creeping over me. I have a bad habit of losing myself in my thoughts when I'm in a bad mood. "


translate English day3_q_rs_5fe8013b:


    nar "I don't want to see anyone, not even Ar."


translate English day3_q_rs_0e58d990:


    nar "I just want to go somewhere quiet where I can be alone so I can cool down while filling my already chaotic thoughts with matters that have nothing to do with me."


translate English day3_q_rs_1376433f:


    nar "Like that so-called den of snakes..."


translate English day3_q_rs_476bee73:


    en "I'm not trying to force you to do anything you don't want to... but just know that if you ever need help, I'm always around."


translate English day3_q_rs_325e59f2:


    pl "Appreciate it..."


translate English day3_q_rs_9f59fed6:


    en "Hn?"


translate English day3_q_rs_b34d0662:


    pl "You're a better person than you look, bro."


translate English day3_q_rs_66cac16e:


    en "Heh, I get that a lot..."


translate English day3_q_gr_085d98d9:


    en "{cps=*0.1}Wh-Wh-{/cps}{nw}"


translate English day3_q_gr_c2865bb5:


    extend "Wh-What did you say?!" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_eb3f2a49:


    en "No!{cps=*0.1} What?! {/cps}{nw}" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_25529a11:


    extend "{cps=*0.2}How could you...{/cps}{cps=*2}{nw}" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_51f9f497:


    extend " Absolutely n-n-not!{/cps}" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_8ec4981f:


    nar "My answer causes him to practically jump out of his skin in shock. But his over-the-top expression means I hit the jackpot."


translate English day3_q_gr_7f1c2ac6:


    nar "I feel my formerly grumpy mood vanish, his unexpected reaction bringing a smile to my face."


translate English day3_q_gr_460a8b97:


    pl "Really? So you hate her then?"


translate English day3_q_gr_4f97198f:


    en "Of c-c-course I don't!"


translate English day3_q_gr_eae3fe7c:


    en "I mean! I just... That's not important! "


translate English day3_q_gr_a940f722:


    en "I don't appreciate you talking about my sister like that! She deserves WAY more respect!"


translate English day3_q_gr_9c94bcdb:


    en "Maybe this is a matter of cultural difference, but she's too good of a person to be referred to so crudely..."


translate English day3_q_gr_1058c7f1:


    pl "If your sister's really that sweet, "


translate English day3_q_gr_393932cc:


    pl "then instead of arguing with random strangers, maybe you should spend more time with her, big bro?"


translate English day3_q_gr_d7f67860:


    en "I never gave you permission to call me THAT!" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_b5d85d94:


    en "D-Don't tell me you were this rude in front of the bishop?! He despises impertience more than anything in the world!"


translate English day3_q_gr_042b337d:


    en "The other day, one of the priests didn't reference his title when addressing him. He was fired on the spot and sent back to where he came from... Gah! He's so rude!"


translate English day3_q_gr_35dab1b0:


    pl "Don't I know it..."


translate English day3_q_gr_aaf2c9cd:


    en "Ugh! He really is an overly-sensitive monster..."


translate English day3_q_gr_b978e18b:


    en "Ahem! Anyway! No matter how far you've come to be here, there's a certain way of doing things that you must adhere to!"


translate English day3_q_gr_a60bb6fb:


    en "Each department has a hierachy and you must always consider your place in every interaction! If you're not familiar with the way we speak here, then study harder..."


translate English day3_q_gr_66d488ce:


    en "...Also, I'm more than happy to help. If you want..."


translate English day3_q_gr_bdd54802:


    pl "Um, what? I've been speaking the language here just fine?"


translate English day3_q_gr_0cd52227:


    en "Huh?"


translate English day3_q_gr_53bdf488:


    pl "Look, I get it. So what you're saying is the bishop of the Magic Department is an irredeemable old fart, "


translate English day3_q_gr_09b180e5:


    pl "and big brother Enoch wants to stand out in his big sister's eyes by pretending to be nice to the rookie who arrived yesterday."


translate English day3_q_gr_5553fdc3:


    en "What?!"


translate English day3_q_gr_a0e1d073:


    pl "Don't worry! From now on, I'll be sure that everyone knows how much I look up to you, dear Enoch! "


translate English day3_q_gr_6203e4d1:


    pl "So don't be so hard on me, big brother of mine... You're sounding just like that bishop you love so much."


translate English day3_q_gr_7f03c3c8:


    en "Wh-What exactly do you mean by THAT?!"


translate English day3_q_gr_7837c90a:


    en "And stop coming up with weird nicknames for me without asking my permission first!" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_b5c6fd4d:


    en "Finally, stop using His Excellency's name as an insult!" with sshake


translate English day3_q_gr_f8191717:


    nar "Seeing this guy so insecure that I fear for his future brings back memories of my village. I had a tendency to irritate everyone with my smart alec remarks."


translate English day3_q_gr_0c946978:


